    • Constructor Detail

      • BlobPair

        BlobPair(float distance,
         Blob newBlob,
         MovingBlob oldBlob)
        Creates a BlobPair from a Blob and MovingBlob in adjacent frames. Many BlobPairs are created during the Blob matching process to match MovingBlobs with their Blob counterparts in subsequent frames.
        Parameters:
        distance - The distance between the two Blobs
        newBlob - The Blob in the current frame
        oldBlob - The Blob from the previous frame
